> [!CAUTION]
> **This page has the most issues in the observer module:**
> 1. Legacy `useQuery` hook (the only page using it)
> 2. Raw `api.patch()` instead of typed helper
> 3. `console.error` in production code
> 4. No cross-query cache invalidation
