## 6. Cross-Role Data Flow Summary

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Observer Actions
        A[Create Timeline Event] --> |visible to| HN[Head Nurse Dashboard]
        A --> |visible to| SV[Supervisor Timeline]
        B[Send Workflow Message] --> |recipient: head_nurse| HN
        C[Submit Handover] --> |target: head_nurse| HN
        D[Update Task Status] --> |visible to| HN
        D --> |visible to| SV
        E[Shift Checklist] --> |personal only| OB[Observer Dashboard]
    end
```

**Verdict**: The Patient Detail page (`patients/[id]`) has **excellent cross-role integration** — all 5 mutations correctly target other roles and invalidate caches. The Tasks page is the **weakest link** and needs refactoring.

